<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>791</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>hái gǔ yào fù huó 迦南791</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yóu tài rén kū qì guò, yóu tài rén xǐng wù guò,
 yǒu jiā wú guó, jiù huì bèi chóu dí tūn méi.
 yǒu guó cái yǒu jiā ya, yǒu jiā cái yǒu nǐ hé wǒ.
 wǒ men cái néng huó xià qù, chéng wèi yǒng bù miè de huǒ.
 shén de guó yào jiàng lín, dì xiōng zài méi yǒu fēn gē.
 mǎn shān biàn yě de hái gǔ, dōu yào fù huó.
 jīn yǔ jīn xiāng jiē ya, gǔ yǔ gǔ lián luò.
 chéng wèi jí dà de jūn duì, yào zǒu xiàng liè guó.</lyrics>
</song>